item.title: The One for Women
item.dc:creator: Zain Saeed
item.description: The One for Women is the only journal with a Fall and Spring Edition. This journal is great for self reflection and mental health. Women will have the opportunity to write some affirmations. Affirmations are positive things you like about yourself, mantras you want to affirm about the day, career, or family. This journal is filled with daily prompts to help with self reflection. See an exclusive preview here! item.title: The Prayer One
item.dc:creator: Zain Saeed
item.description:
The Prayer one is FULL COLOR daily prayer journal. Each page is filled with fun colors to help enhance your journaling experience. Pick a Verse of the Day, jot down notes from your Daily devotional, as well as writing what was in your heart that day. One page will help you learn the ACTS prayer model (Adoration, Confession, Thanksgiving, and Supplication). See an exclusive preview here! PaperBack: 26.99 Hardcover: 35.99

item.title: The Guy One
item.dc:creator: Zain Saeed
item.description: The Guy One is called “Small Wins equal Big Gains”. Take your SMALL WINs of the day/ week to equal Big Gains. Small wins are positive things that happened that day. Also, affirmations, which are positive things you like about yourself or mantras you want to affirm about the day, career, or family. At the end of the week, there is a weekly review page where guys will have the opportunity to find their favorite small wins and affirmations of the week. See an exclusive preview here! PaperBack: 13.99 Hardcover: 19.99 Buy The Guy One
